The maximum depth of birch lake is 47 feet not 35 feet as noted on the information summary sheet.
Cloudy- no white caps but a little breezy.
Partly cloudy with waves but no white caps.
Sunny to partly sunny with a little chop on the water.
Sunny and windy.  We had a lot of rain this last week and the lake level went up 2-3- inches.
Sunny and nice.  Complete ice out on 4-07-98.
Partly cloudy and calm.  About 75 degrees.
Partly sunny- air temp is 50 degrees F. 10 mph wind. Collected one sample BLDH-1. Paid by lake association full suite.
Sunny- 60 degrees F temperature. Took TP sample. Memorial day. DRB assisted.
Partly sunny. Air temp is 90 degrees F. Winds 10-15 mph. Scattered thunderstorms.TP and Chl. DB and EB assisted.
Overcast- 65 degrees F is air temp. DRB assisted. TP and Chl. BLDH -3.
Overcast- 70 F.  Last few days hot- humid.  First cool day in a while.
Partly cloudy conditions made Secchi Disk difficult to see.
Sky was partly cloudy and windy with 8 inch waves.
Sky was somewhat overcast with wind which may have negatively affected the the secchi reading.
Conditions were party cloudy with substantial wind.
Conditions were partly cloudy with a light wind.
Conditions were modestly overcast with a light wind.
The day was slightly overcast with a moderate wind.
Slightly overcast with light wind. Slightly overcast with a light wind. We

Beautiful Day- slightly overcast with light wind
A beautiful sunny day with light wind. A beautiful sunny day with light wind
